import { Flex, Stack, Button, Image, Heading, Text } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import { Link } from "react-router-dom";
import analysis from "../../img/analysis.svg";

const HomePage = () => {
    return (
        <Flex
            align="center"
            justify="space-around"
            wrap="wrap"
            m="auto"
            p="2rem"
            w={1400}
            gap="2rem"
        >
            <Stack
                flex="1 1 auto"
            >
                <Heading>Resume Rater</Heading>
                <Text>
                    Utilizing natural language processing to make your
                    job searching easier.
                </Text>
                <Button>
                    <Link to="/rate">
                        Get Started
                    </Link>
                </Button>
            </Stack>
            <Image 
                flex="1 1.2 auto"
                src={analysis} 
                alt={"woman looking at an analysis"}
            />
        </Flex>
    );
}

export default HomePage;
